{
  "id": "RAW_4377d336",
  "title": "Liquid Glass 支持调整效果、滑动取消闹钟……iOS 26.1 都更新了什么？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU4Mjg3MDAyMQ==&mid=2247599677&idx=1&sn=4a7babe68f445dbebba618f207a0744f",
  "date": "2025-11-06 04:32:00",
  "author": "少数派",
  "siteName": "少数派",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>Vanilla</span> <span>2025-11-06 12:32</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">广东</span></p>\n  <p>iOS 26.1 中值得关注的新特性</p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ffcfc736&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjJISIvRlBryCNHw2ExDDMU42OFayUK4a2pcP9vpOYx1cr8X0zdCuQrzVct3BH9xA1pRfVyxfRZLg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">北京时间 11 月 4 日凌晨，Apple 面向所有适配机型的 iPhone 和 iPad 推送了 iOS 26 正式发布后的第一个大更新。在这个新版本中，Apple 为我们带来了诸多贴心的设置新选项和实用的应用新功能，不少改动都可以从此改变我们的 iPhone 使用习惯。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">接下来，就让我们一起来看看本次 iOS 26.1 版本的更新内容吧。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100115530\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2000\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=71c64bc4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Foylw20gGnRh2Bbibboz1kiatbtur5x5BxfbsxuIALOMib1iaPYW8Q6NfJJP91PUoYW8licytbmutGjgiaWiaoawvLmLAg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h3&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;ss-hIdChildren-1&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;s1&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">▍</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">贴心的设置新选项</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Liquid Glass 显示风格自 iOS 26 推出后，就颇具争议。很多用户都表示不喜欢这种系统风格，甚至认为这种显示风格徒增功耗，降低了手机的运行性能。在 iOS 26.1 版本中，Apple 在系统设置的「显示与亮度」中新增了一个 Liquid Glass 的入口，点击进入后可以切换透明和色调两个选项，前者不用多说，就是默认的液态玻璃显示效果，后者则可以增加显示的不透明度和对比度。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116003\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.0848214285714286\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=895669ba&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjJISIvRlBryCNHw2ExDDMUsEZ9SANl6VVWKBtxLQ57hHPfuUCUaatXj3s2V40mx8ricr6AiaJticxAA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">我相信很多人都遇到过将手机从口袋里拿出来的时候发现相机应用开启的情况，很多时候手机都会因为长时间启动相机而发热明显。新版本中，Apple 非常贴心地在「设置」&gt;「相机」中提供了一个「轻扫锁定屏幕打开相机」的开关，点击关闭后就无法在锁定屏幕中通过轻扫来快速打开相机，这样一来 iPhone 的相机应用就不会再被误打开了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116004\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.0848214285714286\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5c4edbb1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjJISIvRlBryCNHw2ExDDMUn8UkZR7pDJj7erTqwkBaY3aAxVjnVwHLXbIaibLSiaLFqtUePCDGsHdQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">自 iOS 26 版本中优化了闹钟和计时器的触发界面后，Apple 在新版本中又「优化」了关闭闹钟的按钮。一直以来，我们只需要点击「关闭」按钮就可以关闭闹钟，而现在 Apple 给关闭闹钟设置了一点障碍，「关闭」按钮被改成了滑动关闭，这样一来可以避免闹钟不小心被关闭。至于这个改动是否实用，我觉得见仁见智吧。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116005\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"2.174107142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" style=\"width: 332px;height: 722px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=49f61395&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjJISIvRlBryCNHw2ExDDMUDddZT4wmLMFVHLayy3C1GK2NuO15NuOfHiaxuxPRx3YPFc2AdwXOEVg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">很多人都没有注意到当我们接听电话或者挂断电话时，iPhone 会发出轻微的一下震动。如果你不喜欢这个震动，那么可以在「设置」&gt;「电话」中关闭「触感反馈」这个选项。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116006\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"2.174107142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" style=\"width: 337px;height: 733px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ab0312f5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjJISIvRlBryCNHw2ExDDMUwq7J8iaqliccNxVfzWbVdfwutH9qx9Bxaxo1AJEzv4mTIIyEYOXm3Hmg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">为了提高 iOS 系统的安全性，Apple 还在「设置」&gt;「隐私与安全」中新增了一个「安全改进」的选项，启用「自动安装」后可以在后台自动安装 Apple 推送的安全改进，而无需等待 iOS 版本更新。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116007\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"2.174107142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" style=\"width: 363px;height: 789px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=11a4111d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjJISIvRlBryCNHw2ExDDMUyibsnG9cpQ4SuQfGKAn2lYUTXHpic3MUibLkibootjY66agqQuibfBHDHtQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h3&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;ss-hIdChildren-1&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;s1&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">▍</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">实用的应用新功能</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Apple Music 在新版本中也获得了更新。首先，我们可以通过 Apple Music 界面底部的播放控制栏来进行滑动切歌这个操作。与传统的「点击下一曲按钮」相比，滑动切歌操作同时支持向前切歌和向后切歌，滑动的触发区域也比下一曲按钮大很多，提高了切歌操作的效率。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">其次，iOS 26 全新推出的自动过渡功能也在 26.1 版本中支持了 AirPlay，这样在 HomePod、Apple TV 等支持 AirPlay 协议的设备上也可以使用自动过渡的歌曲过渡效果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116008\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.778125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=009d968b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2Foylw20gGnRjJISIvRlBryCNHw2ExDDMUjAE4jn6YZQslAz4nxLq5MRnYudLWqnsM0K98OqsYZbL1IVricIqvqAA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Apple 自家的视频流媒体服务 Apple TV 也是办得越来越有声有色，iOS 26.1 中对 Apple TV 进行了「战略升级」。一方面，Apple TV 启用了全新的图标和 Liquid Glass 设计风格；另一方面，Apple TV 应用内的 Apple TV+ 被简化为 Apple TV，代表着 Apple TV 流媒体服务已经成为了 TV 应用最重要的部分。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116009\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.0848214285714286\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6179734e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjJISIvRlBryCNHw2ExDDMUMGYXy4Oj68QPL40mPyRMibibrJBq72BJ5c7ibDuT56ibRicXR0gN465Yeog%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">如果你是一名运动爱好者，那么健身应用在新版本中推出的自定义锻炼计划创建功能一定会让你感到欣喜。一般情况下，我们只能通过健身应用开启训练或者第三方应用导入来记录锻炼，如果你忘记了开启训练，那就麻烦了，只能通过「快捷指令」来进行曲线救国。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">新版本中，我们可以在健身应用的「体能训练」标签页点击右上角的创建按钮，然后依次选择体能训练的类型、持续时间、开始时间、动态卡路里和耗能情况，最后点击对号按钮即可完成录入。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116010\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.0848214285714286\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d0e6fe94&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjJISIvRlBryCNHw2ExDDMULeSmZ5TAzPUyXe90TWibkGREkk1pTyxUQ0Z8SEic3EQTD4tQzOgUuHcg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h3&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;ss-hIdChildren-1&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;s1&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">▍</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">其它更新内容</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">除了设置新选项和应用新功能，Apple 在新版本中还对一些系统中的界面重新进行了设计。比如说，设置界面中所有包含文本的设置项都统一为说明文本左对齐，同时主屏幕上的文件夹名称也统一为左对齐，达成了系统级的一致。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116011\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.7241071428571428\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=72a97665&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjJISIvRlBryCNHw2ExDDMUJwPhx5XlssyFOjXQy619T9QWTftt7OgYuN0ic8vgicSKic8uABPcTZlRg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">照片应用中的一些元素也在新版本中进行了视觉上的优化。首先，控制视频播放的滑动条进行了重新设计；其次，照片应用底部的导航栏采用了略带磨砂质感的外观，使其在浅色图片上更容易被看清楚；最后，对多张照片进行批量处理的操作界面也全面焕新，以幻灯片形式播放、收藏和隐藏这三个按钮都被置顶成一排单独显示。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116012\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.7241071428571428\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7af970f7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjJISIvRlBryCNHw2ExDDMUCViaGt4VsnIPOyzCno052chI7bKG5icMFKkoiceeuZOicIr5lpZh5OZSXg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">在 iOS 26.1 中，通过系统设置中的「通用」&gt;「本地采集」选项，现在可以指定录制通话或视频会议后文件的保存位置，也可以选择在录制视频会议时仅保留音频文件。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116013\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"2.1714285714285713\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" style=\"width: 348px;height: 756px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f08c3ba9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjJISIvRlBryCNHw2ExDDMUtGauwqLJPYyUvTWJjRyWTic8PUEOVkA4KnHLsqmSAKhrX6icdGxn4iaBg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">iPadOS 在新版本中也有一个较大的变化，那就是 Slide Over 功能重新加入了 iPadOS 中，这样一来多任务处理场景下又多了一个实用的功能，可以与原先的多窗口模式兼容。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116014\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=078609db&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjJISIvRlBryCNHw2ExDDMUfqo0AzHyBSlp2xocCb2utHtnhtUXeoJgalTUOYGgAEozUSyo7b7Sbw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(84, 84, 84);\">图片来源：MacRumors</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h3&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;ss-hIdChildren-1&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;s1&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">▍</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">Apple Intelligence</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">最后，我们来简单聊一聊与中国大陆地区的国行用户依旧无缘的 Apple Intelligence 新功能。在 iOS 26.1 中，Apple Intelligence 新增了 8 种语言支持，分别是丹麦语、荷兰语、挪威语、葡萄牙语（葡萄牙）、瑞典语、土耳其语、繁体中文和越南语版本。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">不过，我更关心的是 AirPods 实时翻译在新版本中终于支持了中文，包括简体和繁体普通话。刚好我使用的在海外购买的 iPhone，也简单体验了一下这个功能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">第一次使用时，我们需要在翻译 app 的实时标签页中选择对方语言和你的语言，选择好后应用会开始下载相应的语言包文件。下载好语言包后，戴上 AirPods 耳机并点击开始翻译，翻译应用会开始实时监听外界的声音，然后将听到的语言翻译成我的语言在耳机中播放给我，同时也会在屏幕上实时显示两种语言的字幕。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">以英语翻译为中文为例，我选择了 Apple TV 上的《The Morning Show》来测试，结果是受限于语速和长句等原因，实时翻译并不能完整地监听并记录到语句，导致实时翻译的结果并不如人意，希望 Apple 能在后续的版本迭代中优化一下监听的体验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100116015\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.08125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e0c69787&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRjJISIvRlBryCNHw2ExDDMURJa8KbqjxGT4wm9uCVtNicsjAZusOGZHmtHutH3hIsOWJASrUDXmFqA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">以上就是本次 iOS 26.1 更新的主要内容，如果你还发现了其它有价值的更新内容，欢迎大家在评论区一起分享和交流。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-left: 8px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-size-adjust: auto;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(84, 84, 84);color: rgb(84, 84, 84);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">原文链接：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-left: 8px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-size-adjust: auto;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(84, 84, 84);color: rgb(84, 84, 84);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://sspai.com/post/103538?utm_source=wechat&amp;utm_medium=social\" target=\"_blank\">https://sspai.com/post/103538?utm_source=wechat&amp;utm_medium=social</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-left: 8px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-size-adjust: auto;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(84, 84, 84);color: rgb(84, 84, 84);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\"